<br>
<b>Educational Objectives:</b><br> 
ARC will produce graduates who have:
<ul>
    <li>intellectual abilities with balanced personalities</li>
    <li>leadership abilities in multicultural settings</li>
    <li>religious and moral values</li>
    <li>strong communication skills and competencies in using modern technological tools</li>
    <li>abilities for life-long learning and desire for personal/professional excellence</li>
</ul>